data.name: sqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [staff] ([staffID], [stf_Name], [stf_Gender], [stf_phoneNo], [stf_Join], [stf_Position], [stf_Age]) VALUES (@staffID, @stf_Name, @stf_Gender, @stf_phoneNo, @stf_Join, @stf_Position, @stf_Age); SELECT staffID, stf_Name, stf_Gender, stf_phoneNo, stf_Join, stf_Position, stf_Age FROM staff WHERE (staffID = @staffID)
